  "blocks": [
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": "Nepalgunj Municipality was established in 2017 B.S. according to historical records. Following the declaration of the sub-metropolis on 2071/08/16 B.S., 28 former wards were consolidated into the current 13 wards. This administrative restructuring reflects the city's expansion and its central role in the federal governance system of Nepal."
